high_descs: Go around the table to the side facing the sofa.
Pick up the closest remote on the right side.
Turn around and face to sofa.
Place the remote on the sofa in front of the keys to the right of the red cushion.
Turn around and go to the right side of the table.
Pick up the other remote on the table.
Go back to the sofa.
Place the remote on the left of the first remote.

Place the remote on the couch in front of the keys.

Pick up the remote on the table.
Turn left and walk back to the center cushion of the couch.
Place the remote to the left of the other remote.
anns.task_desc: Place two remotes on a couch.

high_descs: Approach the coffee table in the middle of the room.

Turn around and face the coffee table.
